<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Donate — Vihaan's Vision</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
</head>
<body>

<header class="topbar">
  <a class="brand" href="/" aria-label="Vihaan's Vision home">
    <span class="logo-mark">☀️</span>
    <span class="logo-copy">
      <strong>Vihaan's Vision</strong>
      <small>A world where every child smiles</small>
    </span>
  </a>
  <nav>
    <a href="/">Home</a><a href="/events/">Events</a><a href="/donate/" style="color:#2f6f9f">Donate</a><a href="/donation-events/">Donation Events</a><a href="/team/">Team</a><a href="/contact/">Contact Us</a>
  </nav>
</header>


<main>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <span class="kicker">Donate</span>
    <h1 class="page-title">Help turn filament into smiles.</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Donations support materials and supplies used to create 3D-printed keychains, toys,
      and future gifts for children. AI class donations also help fund this mission.
    </p>
    <div class="actions">
      <a class="btn primary" href="https://hcb.hackclub.com/donations/start/vihaan-s-vision" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Make a Donation</a>
      <a class="btn light" href="/donation-events/">View Donation Events</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2 class="section-title">What Donations Support</h2>
    <div class="grid-3">
      <article class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">🧵</div>
        <h3>3D Printing Materials</h3>
        <p>Filament, colors, replacement parts, and supplies needed to make the gifts.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">📦</div>
        <h3>Packaging</h3>
        <p>Gift bags, cards, labels, and safe packaging so every item feels special.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">🚚</div>
        <h3>Delivery & Events</h3>
        <p>Helping prepare and deliver donated items to children and partner organizations.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="band">
    <div class="callout">
      <h2>Every donation becomes something a child can hold.</h2>
      <p>
        A small contribution can help create keychains, toys, bookmarks, and future creative gifts.
        The goal is not just to make objects — it is to create a moment of joy.
      </p>

      <div class="stat-row">
        <div class="stat">$15<br><small>filament support</small></div>
        <div class="stat">$25<br><small>gift batch support</small></div>
        <div class="stat">$50<br><small>event support</small></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="donation-form">
    <h2 class="section-title">Donation Interest Form</h2>
    <p class="section-intro">
      Send a note about how you would like to support Vihaan's Vision.
    </p>

    <form class="form" action="#" method="post">
      <div class="split">
        <div class="form-row">
          <label for="donor-name">Name</label>
          <input id="donor-name" name="donor-name" type="text" placeholder="Your name" required />
        </div>

        <div class="form-row">
          <label for="donor-email">Email</label>
          <input id="donor-email" name="donor-email" type="email" placeholder="Your email" required />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="form-row">
        <label for="donation-subject">Subject</label>
        <input id="donation-subject" name="donation-subject" type="text" placeholder="Donation support / materials / partnership" required />
      </div>

      <div class="form-row">
        <label for="donation-info">Info</label>
        <textarea id="donation-info" name="donation-info" rows="6" placeholder="Tell us how you would like to help"></textarea>
      </div>

      <button class="btn primary" type="submit">Send Donation Message</button>
    </form>
  </section>
</main>

<footer>
  <p>☀️ A world where every child smiles — one gift, one child, one ray at a time.</p>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
